    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/119a64fdb7663142da1a6bb0cb5c3df2.webp?t=1745507868\" width=616 height=52 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncursed</strong> is a first-person psychological horror game blending immersive storytelling, environmental exploration, and puzzle-solving. Navigate a house filled with unsettling secrets, uncover the dark past hidden beneath its walls, and escape before history repeats itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/89fc821f8dd426086b3d1b3a7dd3eebe.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/89fc821f8dd426086b3d1b3a7dd3eebe.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/89fc821f8dd426086b3d1b3a7dd3eebe.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Alex</i></strong> thought he had left his past behind. But when his <i>grandmother</i> stops answering his calls, he returns home—only to find a place warped by time, filled with eerie remnants of forgotten rituals and a creeping presence that watches from the dark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As he unravels the mystery surrounding his family, the walls begin to shift, shadows twist into something unnatural, and the truth he seeks may not be one he can survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/33bfd01d1d5475522a52c57eaa78681a.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/33bfd01d1d5475522a52c57eaa78681a.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/33bfd01d1d5475522a52c57eaa78681a.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With spine-tingling atmosphere, intense jump scares, and a haunting storyline, <strong>UNCURSED</strong> will keep you on the edge of your seat from start to finish. Can you survive the horrors that await you? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/e875f0bae0202a24a72855a6b8bc008a.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/e875f0bae0202a24a72855a6b8bc008a.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/e875f0bae0202a24a72855a6b8bc008a.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/07923337404949a88c038e231f4e086b.webp?t=1745507868\" width=616 height=52 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles in UNCURSED are designed to be challenging but fair. They will require you to use your wits and logic to solve them. There is a variety of puzzles in the game, including:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Logic puzzles:</strong> These puzzles will require you to use your reasoning skills to solve them. For example, you may need to figure out a code or solve a mathematical equation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/6eac12b96cef0667852fa853700504f4.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/6eac12b96cef0667852fa853700504f4.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/6eac12b96cef0667852fa853700504f4.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inventory puzzles:</strong> These puzzles will require you to use items from your inventory in order to solve them. For example, you may need to combine two items to create a new item.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/00e5ec615ee0f06e30772eca29e788e5.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/00e5ec615ee0f06e30772eca29e788e5.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/00e5ec615ee0f06e30772eca29e788e5.mp4?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹 <strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Haunting Story – Unravel a mystery filled with loss, forgotten rituals, and the horrors of the past.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Ever-Changing House – The environment twists and distorts as Alex uncovers buried secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration &amp; Puzzle Solving – Search for clues, unlock hidden passages, and piece together the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unseen Forces – Feel the presence stalking you, hear whispers that were never meant for you, and question what is real.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/6d58b966a3f4d77647564de4f866f96f.webp?t=1745507868\" width=616 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong> – Every choice matters. Will you break the <strong>curse</strong>, or will it <strong>consume you</strong>?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/f871915ec154ae6b95edd4f090d52cb0.poster.avif?t=1745507868\" width=800 height=271 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316910/extras/f871915ec154ae6b95edd4f090d52cb0.webm?t=1745507868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
